trans-unit.source: RawSecureSocket provides a secure (SSL or TLS) network connection. Client connections to a server are provided by calling RawSecureSocket.connect. A secure server, created with RawSecureServerSocket, also returns RawSecureSocket objects representing the server end of a secure connection. The certificate provided by the server is checked using the trusted certificates set in the SecurityContext object. The default SecurityContext object contains a built-in set of trusted root certificates for well-known certificate authorities.
trans-unit.target: RawSecureSocket提供安全的（SSL或TLS）网络连接。通过调用RawSecureSocket.connect提供与服务器的客户端连接。使用RawSecureServerSocket创建的安全服务器还返回代表安全连接服务器端的RawSecureSocket对象。使用SecurityContext对象中设置的受信任证书检查服务器提供的证书。默认的SecurityContext对象包含一组内置的受信任的根证书，用于知名证书颁发机构。
